  "body": "#### System information\n\nGeth version: 1.4\nOS & Version: OSX\nCommit hash : 8241fa5\n\nIn this latest version it doesn't detect old keyhole (folder) formats anymore. This brings a lot of inconvenience for people, as we have no way to import this old formats, nor a way to export them in an older version.\n\nWe definitely need to add a way to import those old formats, if we remove support for them..\n",
